      • protobufVersion

        public String protobufVersion
        Protobuf version to compile schema files for. If omitted, version is inferred from the project's depended-on com.google.com:protobuf-java artifact, if any. (If both are present, the version must match.)

      • protocExec

        public File protocExec

      • jsOnly

        public String[] jsOnly
        Protobuf packages to only compile only to JS. If a package appears on the jsOnly and javaOnly lists then it will be compiled to both.

      • javaOnly

        public String[] javaOnly
        Protobuf packages to only compile only to Java. If a package appears on the jsOnly and javaOnly lists then it will be compiled to both.
